snippet.title: Davidd Tech
snippet.description:
Testing Trading Strategies with code.
Hey, I'm Davidd. Yep with two D's.  😏 I was told that the double D was Welsh but I have a funny feeling my parents were just 🥴 🍺🍷 🥳 . Anyway, we will keep that story for another day 😳. 

I began the DaviddTech channel as a way to share my 20 years trading and coding experience and passion for the code. Which brought me to purchasing Bitcoin. Since that day I have dedicated my life to making trading strategies in code.

Twitter: @DaviddDotTech
Instagram: @DaviddTech

So, let's talk traders!
